3. cs.DC - The paper discusses the architecture for connecting the Jason agent platform to the Apache Camel enterprise integration framework, which involves distributed computing. 
4. cs.DL - The paper discusses the design of agent percept, action, and message endpoints, which could involve deep learning techniques. 
5. cs.PL - The paper discusses the benefits of interfacing agents to external services via a specialized message routing tool, which could involve programming language concepts.
